<resources xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools">
    <!--
        My device: Samsung Note 20 Ultra
        My android version: 12
        My Screen Resolution: FHD+

        Use the landscape mode
        In Landscape mode, the values X and Y are inverted

        Portrait:
        Device Width: X => 1080
        Device Height: Y => 2316

        Landscape:
        Device Width: X => 2316
        Device Height: Y => 1080

        Find the dimensions of your device in MainActivity ( DEBUG )

        Add the android:background="@color/colorAlphaWhite" in layout ( RelativeLayout ) to help the adjusts

        You may need to make adjustments to the buttons
    -->

